Targeting BCR-ABL-Independent TKI Resistance in Chronic Myeloid Leukemia by mTOR 
and Autophagy Inhibition.

Mitchell R(1), Hopcroft LEM(2), Baquero P(1), Allan EK(3), Hewit K(4), James 
D(4), Hamilton G(5), Mukhopadhyay A(2), O'Prey J(4), Hair A(2), Melo JV(6), Chan 
