969. BMC Pediatr. 2017 Nov 22;17(1):195. doi: 10.1186/s12887-017-0947-0.

Pediatric hospital admissions in Indigenous children: a population-based study 
in remote Australia.

Dossetor PJ(1)(2)(3), Martiniuk ALC(4)(5)(6), Fitzpatrick JP(7)(8), Oscar 
J(9)(10), Carter M(11), Watkins R(8), Elliott EJ(7)(12)(13), Jeffery HE(14)(6), 
Harley D(15)(16).

Author information:
(1)Clinical Medical School, College of Medicine, Biology & Environment, 
Australian National University, 97/2 Edinburgh Ave, Canberra, ACT, 2601, 
